        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="legend_txt" value="&lt;font style='font-size:9px'&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Budget&lt;/b&gt; = module in Provisioning (new tables: FinancialCalendar, CompanyBudget, etc.; budget_routes.py).&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Approval&lt;/b&gt; = new microservice (8008): chains, workflow instances, routing, escalation. Same DB, schema approval.&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Order&lt;/b&gt; = new Order/OrderRequest in Provisioning; submit triggers policy then approval when require_approval.&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Graph&lt;/b&gt; = extended with eligible-approvers query for routing.&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#555;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="95" y="555" width="370" height="68" as="geometry" />
